# Deferred Tools Loading

Use only tool names exposed by the current Antigravity CLI runtime. Load a schema
through the platform's native discovery surface before the first deferred call.
If discovery does not expose a requested tool, stop that route with an
unsupported-tool diagnostic; never substitute a primitive from another agent
platform.

Persistent Claude team lifecycle is not supported on this platform. `--team`
must fail closed and direct the user to the ordinary Antigravity subagent
pipeline. Do not emit guessed team creation, direct teammate messaging, or team
deletion calls.
